Subject: Re: [racket-bug] all/11160: loaded teachpacks must be Run before available
Date: Sat, 4 Sep 2010 06:32:57 -0500

 What is the right thing to do here?
 
  a) load the teachpacks in that first run
  b) not display the teachpacks in that first run
  c) do not display the teachpacks at all
 
 Robby
 
