Subject: Re: [racket-bug] all/11160: loaded teachpacks must be Run before available
Date: Sat, 4 Sep 2010 11:00:23 -0400

 (b) doesn't make sense to me because if the student then hit F5, the
 Teachpacks would appear.  So there is state that is being hidden, and
 hiding it might be confusing: the Teachpack is there, but I don't see
 it, so I go to add it, but it's already added.  It seems to me the
 first REPL should act as if someone had already hit F5.
 
