 I'm sure you know most of this, Shriram, but the exercise of us
 getting "#lang htdp/isl" going is going to make this path smoother for
 those not familiar with the guts of Racket and don't have the energy
 to become so (like you) but (and this is where you may be
 disappointed) I don't think that the stepper is ever going to be
 language independent. At least not without research.
 
 Robby
 
